Matching World-Class Research with Industry Leaders
At the Office of Corporate and Institutional Partnerships, we believe that collaboration drives innovation. We work closely with faculty and researchers to keep up with the latest developments emerging from our pioneering labs and centers. Strategic partnerships at Carnegie Mellon provide your organization with unparalleled access to cutting-edge research, and provide our students with invaluable real-world experience.
Follow the links below to read about our most successful partnerships or contact us directly to learn about how your business can benefit from our expertise.
